json-fortran
------------------------------------------
A user-friendly, thread-safe, and object-oriented API for reading and writing
JSON files, written in modern Fortran.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.6-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libgfortran5-13.4.0-1
  libjsonfortran-devel-9.2.0-1bl1
  libjsonfortran9.2-9.2.0-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.45.1-1
  cmake-4.1.3-1
  cygport-0.37.6-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-fortran-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/jacobwilliams/json-fortran

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/jacobwilliams/json-fortran/archive/refs/tags/9.2.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack json-fortran-9.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./json-fortran-9.2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/json-fortran-9.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/json-fortran-9.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libjsonfortran9.2-9.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libjsonfortran-devel-9.2.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(json-fortran)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/json-fortran.README
  /usr/share/doc/json-fortran/CHANGELOG.md
  /usr/share/doc/json-fortran/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/json-fortran/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/json-fortran/json-fortran.md
  /usr/share/doc/json-fortran/media/json-fortran-32x32.png
  /usr/share/doc/json-fortran/media/json-fortran-logo-2.png
  /usr/share/doc/json-fortran/media/json-fortran-logo-2.svg
  /usr/share/doc/json-fortran/media/json-fortran-logo-250px.png
  /usr/share/doc/json-fortran/media/json-fortran-logo.svg

(libjsonfortran9.2)
  /usr/bin/cygjsonfortran-9.2.dll

(libjsonfortran-devel)
  /usr/include/json-fortran/json_file_module.mod
  /usr/include/json-fortran/json_kinds.mod
  /usr/include/json-fortran/json_module.mod
  /usr/include/json-fortran/json_parameters.mod
  /usr/include/json-fortran/json_string_utilities.mod
  /usr/include/json-fortran/json_value_module.mod
  /usr/lib/cmake/json-fortran/jsonfortran-gnu-config-version.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/json-fortran/jsonfortran-gnu-config.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/json-fortran/jsonfortran-gnu-targets-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/json-fortran/jsonfortran-gnu-targets.cmake
  /usr/lib/libjsonfortran.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/json-fortran.pc

